cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
